rows.label: qst001702_msg001
rows.name: Oh, I'm rushed off my feet here!

rows.label: qst001702_msg002
rows.name:
I went to the trouble of putting a flyer
up at Nharil Central Plaza, but did
anyone bother to read it, I wonder?

rows.label: qst001702_msg003
rows.name:
Ugh, not that I have time to be fretting
about things like that...

rows.label: qst001702_msg004
rows.name:
I'd better get my report written up.
It might impact on the budget for the
next quarter.

rows.label: qst001702_msg0101
rows.name:
Oh! These are Whitescale Antennae,
are they not?

rows.label: qst001702_msg0102
rows.name:
And exactly three, no less! Excellent!
Perhaps you saw the flyer?

rows.label: qst001702_msg0103
rows.name: Ah, I see. Well, it's a big help.

rows.label: qst001702_msg0104
rows.name:
I'm engaged in research of Superbian
fauna, you see.

rows.label: qst001702_msg0105
rows.name:
Naturally, that requires a certain
amount of hands-on work in the
relevant locations.

rows.label: qst001702_msg0106
rows.name:
But sadly, I don't really have the time,
or required martial abilities, to visit the
Thermal Exhaust Fork.

rows.label: qst001702_msg0107
rows.name:
My hands are full with researching a
range of lifeforms. Unfortunately, the
humble Noog Vang has a lower priority.

rows.label: qst001702_msg0108
rows.name:
However, if you have the Whitescale
Antennae from the Noog Vang, then it's
enough for a basic report.

rows.label: qst001702_msg0109
rows.name:
If the information contained in my
report is disseminated throughout the
military...

rows.label: qst001702_msg0110
rows.name:
then no doubt it'll make the job of
taking on those wretched Noog
Vangs quite a bit easier.

rows.label: qst001702_msg0111
rows.name:
Well, I should get to work on my
report.

rows.label: qst001702_msg0112
rows.name:
Oh, and here is your reward. I'm very
glad that you responded to my request,
so thanks again!
